# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:4
translate portuguese work0_f28cee14:

    # "Immediately after finishing up my classes for the day, I head out to the car and drive over to the Law Offices, where my new job is."
    "Imediatamente após terminar as aulas do dia, dirijo-me ao carro e conduzo até ao escritório de advocacia, onde é o meu novo emprego."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:7
translate portuguese work0_5a8d723c:

    # "I walk in to work. Dana is sitting in the lobby. I wave hello to her."
    "Entro no trabalho. A Dana está sentada no átrio. Aceno-lhe em sinal de cumprimento."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:8
translate portuguese work0_468fc973:

    # cw "Hey there new guy. [pcname], wasn't it?"
    cw "Olá, novato. [pcname], não era?"

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:9
translate portuguese work0_749220c3:

    # pc "That's me."
    pc "Sou eu."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:10
translate portuguese work0_9e8ad45b:

    # cw "Mrs. Mills is back in her office. Go right ahead. Hope you have a good day."
    cw "A Sra. Mills está no seu escritório. Passe à frente. Espero que tenha um bom dia."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:11
translate portuguese work0_efe7c8fa:

    # pc "Thanks, you too."
    pc "Obrigado, para si também."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:13
translate portuguese work0_58488fe0:

    # "I go back to Mrs. Mills' office."
    "Volto para o escritório da Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:15
translate portuguese work0_532a1db6:

    # "She sits at her desk, barely glancing up at me when I walk in."
    "Ela está sentada à secretária, mal olhando para mim quando entro."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:17
translate portuguese work0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_goodafternoon.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_goodafternoon.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:18
translate portuguese work0_640a0bfd:

    # bs "Good afternoon. I hope you're ready to work."
    bs "Boa tarde. Espero que esteja pronto para trabalhar."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:19
translate portuguese work0_c24d08f6:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am, I am."
    pc "Sim, senhora, estou."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:20
translate portuguese work0_cc9bf2b9:

    # bs "Good."
    bs "Ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:22
translate portuguese work0_4d725376:

    # "I spend most of the day cleaning. The place had gotten pretty bad over the few weeks where she didn't have an assistant and Mrs. Mills wants the place to be spotless."
    "Passo a maior parte do dia a limpar. O local tinha ficado bastante sujo durante as semanas em que ela não teve assistente e a Sra. Mills quer que o local fique impecável."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:23
translate portuguese work0_e7ab64bb:

    # "I dust everything, wipe every surface, vacuum the floor, and organize all the paperwork."
    "Limpo o pó de tudo, esfrego todas as superfícies, aspiro o chão e organizo toda a papelada."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:25
translate portuguese work0_67f863e2:

    # "Afterwards, Mrs. Mills has me type all her notes while she dictates. Luckily, I'm a fast typist because she is a fast talker and doesn't slow down at all."
    "Depois, a Sra. Mills pede-me para dactilografar todas as suas notas enquanto ela dita. Felizmente, sou um dactilógrafo rápido, porque ela fala depressa e não abranda de todo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:26
translate portuguese work0_cec5844a:

    # "Finally, when it is time to go, she looks over the notes that I had typed and gives a little nod."
    "Finalmente, quando chega a hora de ir embora, ela dá uma olhadela nas notas que eu digitei e acena ligeiramente com a cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:30
translate portuguese work0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:31
translate portuguese work0_7e667a4e:

    # bs "You did good work today. Keep it up and maybe you'll be able to stick around here for a while."
    bs "Fizeste um bom trabalho hoje. Continua assim e talvez consigas ficar por aqui por algum tempo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:32
translate portuguese work0_a9a2d1b9:

    # pc "Thanks."
    pc "Obrigada."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:33
translate portuguese work0_cd3b9566:

    # bs "See you tomorrow."
    bs "Até amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:34
translate portuguese work0_a5da4cbe:

    # pc "Okay, goodbye, Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Está bem, adeus, Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:37
translate portuguese work0_bab3cfa9:

    # "I walk out and down the hall to the lobby. There, Dana is still working, sorting paperwork at her desk."
    "Saio e desço o corredor até ao átrio. Lá, a Dana ainda está a trabalhar, a organizar a papelada na sua secretária."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:38
translate portuguese work0_7c1acf53:

    # pc "Goodnight Dana."
    pc "Boa noite, Dana."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:40
translate portuguese work0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:41
translate portuguese work0_68df17d0:

    # cw "Oh, goodnight, [pcname]. See you tomorrow."
    cw "Oh, boa noite, [pcname]. Até amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:43
translate portuguese work0_ef83833d:

    # "I go outside and stand in front of the building for a moment, breathing the fresh air."
    "Saio e fico em frente ao edifício por um momento, a respirar o ar fresco."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:44
translate portuguese work0_9dec6a30:

    # "It has been a long day and I'm exhausted. And this is only the first. Every weekday is going to be like this basically, leaving me only the evenings to do whatever I want."
    "Foi um dia longo e estou exausta. E este é apenas o primeiro. Basicamente, todos os dias da semana vão ser assim, deixando-me apenas as noites para fazer o que quiser."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:45
translate portuguese work0_d7ac5816:

    # "So, what do I want to do now?"
    "Então, o que é que eu quero fazer agora?"

